tms: The institution from which this degree was granted. This field is required for both local, UCB, or non-UCB Institutions. Validated against Institution (institution) tms table.

The code that further defines the planned gift.  If the pg_type is 'B', the value must exist in the tms bequest type table.  If the pg_type is 'L'   then the value must exist in the tms instrument table. If the pg_type is 'T', then the value must exist in the tms trust code table.

The status of the planned gift.  If the pg_type is 'B', the value must exist in the tms bequest status table.  If the pg_type is 'L'   then the value must exist in the tms life income table. If the pg_type is 'T', then the value must exist in the tms trust status table.
The institution from which this degree was granted. This field is required for both local, UCB, or non-UCB Institutions. Validated against Institution (institution) tms table.
